description:
On a special Thanksgiving episode, Danny recaps the finale of Real Housewives of Orange County & the thrilling trailer for the #RHOC reunion. Comedian Heather McMahan stops by to talk about Britney, Tara Reid, all the Housewives franchises, Vanderpump Rules, and SO much more. Finally, co-host of the "It's Britney Bitch" podcast & WWHL alum T. Kyle calls in for a quick chat about Britney and Housewives.


*To support this podcast and access bonus episodes, go to Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
